Info.Title: Kiki's Delivery Service
Info.Writer: Eiko Kadono (based on the novel by), Satoko Okudera (screenplay), Takashi Shimizu (screenplay)
Info.Actors: Tadanobu Asano, Machiko Ono, Rie Miyazawa, Minako Kotobuki
Info.Plot: A young witch, on her mandatory year of independent life, finds fitting into a new community difficult while she supports herself by running an air courier service.
